http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/andhra-pradesh/Cattle-grazer-drowns-in-village-pond/article13995409.ece

A 26-year-old cattle grazer drowned in a village pond at Sankavaram in Vinjamur mandal limits here on Monday. The victim, Thatiboyina Penchalaiah, along with another person, entered the pond to drive his cattle herd in a direction away from the agricultural fields, abutting the tank. Having his attention on the cattle herd, he did not realise when he went deep into the water. He got entangled in the underwater bushes and drowned, while his friend safely swam ashore. Upon receiving information, police arrived at the spot and fished out the body. .